data.name: EmbedMapUnits
desc: contains list of possible map modes supported by embedded object.

items.name: ONE_100TH_MM
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one-hundredth of millimeter.

items.name: ONE_10TH_MM
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one-tenth of millimeter.

items.name: ONE_MM
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one millimeter.

items.name: ONE_CM
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one centimeter.

items.name: ONE_1000TH_INCH
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one-thousandth of inch.

items.name: ONE_100TH_INCH
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one-hundredth of inch.

items.name: ONE_10TH_INCH
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one-tenth of inch.

items.name: ONE_INCH
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one inch.

items.name: POINT
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one typographical point.

items.name: TWIP
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one twentieth of typographical point.

items.name: PIXEL
lines: In this type of map mode one logical point is equal to one pixel.
